{{Otheruses|Quasar}}
'''Quasar Cargo''' was a company that supplied the [[Liberty Task Force]] after the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] arranged a contract with [[Dunari]].

==Behind the scenes==
Craft of that company are seen in mission 5:2 of ''[[Star Wars: X-Wing Alliance]]'', if the player identifies the craft escorting the [[Liberty/Legends|''Liberty'']], before proceeding to the hyperspace and the main objective of the mission. They exist purely to add realism and consistency to the game (mission 5:1 concerned the arrangement of supplying procedures between the Alliance and Dunari).

